snippet.title: Seafight: Rise of the Submariner!
snippet.description:
Atlantis meets Nautica as submarines rise to the surface and engage pirate ships in PvP and PvE action for the first time.
Be part of this brand new twist to Seafight and take advantage of all the opportunities this new fighting force creates.
The Rise of the Submariner is the next part of our biggest content update ever - Atlantis!
Submarines will be on the surface and will be fighting both alongside and against you!

https://www.seafight.com/
